com.qmetry.qaf.automation.report

Class SourceGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.qmetry.qaf.automation.report.SourceGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TestCaseResultUpdator

    public class SourceGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
implements TestCaseResultUpdator
    This class generates feature files from test implementation even if implementation is in Java. Generated feature file will have examples for data-driven test cases, regardless of test data provider. Generated feature files can be used as proof or to share with other team(s) within project and will enable development team to follow behavior driven development with test automation implementation in best efficient way.
    Author:
    chirag.jayswal
